data.description: Enjoy low maintenance living in this ACTIVE 55+ gated community with events, activities, community pool, and lawn maintenance is included. Built in 2021, this amazing home boasts 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, and a versatile flex room ideal for an additional bedroom or office space. With an airy open layout and tile throughout, this residence offers a contemporary ambiance. The kitchen showcases quartz countertops and a sizable island complete with a breakfast bar. Step onto the delightful enclosed lanai, which leads to a charming paver patio in the fenced backyard. Positioned on a peaceful cul-de-sac, this property is just a short stroll away from convenient amenities. The two-car garage provides ample parking and storage. Schedule a showing today!
